Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:37.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说, 行凶手法\N和杀害劳拉的一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The short answer is, this is the work\Nof the same ghoul who killed Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:38.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有更疯狂的.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More fan mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.96,0:02:41.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是在马蒂指甲下发现的\N字母『O』.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The letter O\Nunder Maddy's ring fingernail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:44.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她右手上还有\N些羽绒毛线.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were strands of fur\Nclutched in her right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:47.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是什么毛?\N- 白狐貍的.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What kind of fur?\N- White fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:50.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,毛线是用甲醛制过的\N动物标本，填塞用的.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strands were laced with\Nformaldehyde. A dead animal, stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll make phone calls. Leland will know\Nhow to get a hold of Maddy's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:55.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我去打几个电话. 利兰该知道\N怎样联系马蒂的家人.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, don't make any calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:56.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 先别急着打电话.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:59.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我需要24小时.\N- 干什么用?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l need 24 hours.\N- For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去了结这事儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:02.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,依我看...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln observation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l don't know where this is headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:11.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...这个案子不知道什么时候才能破.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the only one of us\Nwith coordinates
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们唯一\N对此能达成共识的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for this destination and its hardware\Nis you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:16.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你的确有\N破案的实力.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on whatever vision quest\Nyou require.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样\N继续去追随你的先验吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand on the rim of the volcano,\Nstand alone and do your dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,独自站在火山口,\N跳你的祈求祭祀舞.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just find this beast\Nbefore he takes another bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过，最好在下一个受害者出现之前\N把这只野兽找出来.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God help me,\Nl don't know where to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:34.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,神助我吧,\N我也搞不清路向何方了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:37.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经上路了.\N你不需要知道它向何方.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on the path.\NYou don't need to know where it leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只管跟着它走就是了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought you'd never get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:51.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你不会来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l went for a ride this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:54.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我今早开车去兜风了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, the engine sounded like\Na thousand people singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:57.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊, 引擎的声音美妙的就像\N千人大合唱.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:01.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那他们在唱什么呢?\N- 你觉得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What were they singing about?\N- What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:04.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唱昨晚吗?\N我想是在唱昨晚.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night?\Nl could sing about last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:06.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我有东西给你.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,打开吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 詹姆斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道买什么尺寸的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't know what size to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:25.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那珠宝店的售货女孩\N只有一双大手.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the girl at the jewelry store\Nhad these really big hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我敢打赌...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l'll bet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,绝配.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,James.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:37.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是觉得\N我们应该永远在一起.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just think we should\Nbe together all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:38.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf that's okay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正是我的理想.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:02.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么鸟\N下的蛋啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever fowl\Ndid you take these eggs from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想说很难吃是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we saying we don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm afraid l'm gonna\Nrun into a thumbtack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:07.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么，\N我这么快就成眼中钉了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, can't you ever say\Nanything nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:13.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈, 难道你就\N不能说点好听的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:17.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经很努力了.\N我已经很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've tried so hard.\Nl try so hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and nothing is good enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:19.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何事合你意的.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:23.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己来更正一下, 应该是没有一件\N我做的事合你心意的.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me correct myself, nothing l do\Nis ever good enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:27.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唔, 没有啊.\N这菜牌就做的不错.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's not true.\NThe menus are very presentable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀, 我开玩笑的啦.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l'm joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly,\Nlet me make a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:33.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,说真的,\N我给点建议吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you wanna serve\Na truly memorable omelet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:37.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你做好一份\N真正让人难忘的煎蛋卷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:42.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,试试加点纯小牛肉肠\N和羊肚菌菇.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,try white veal sausage\Nand morel mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:46.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢了. 我会去挑选蘑菇的.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. l'll go pick the mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚说什么来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:08.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没说什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:10.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好, 唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好, 詹姆斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:18.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 法文啊.\N- 我知道是法文, 告诉我.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- lt's French.\N- l know it is, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:20.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 这么紧张干嘛呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Mrs. Tremond?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识屈梦太太吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么小姐?\N- 屈梦太太.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Miss who?\N- Mrs. Tremond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:34.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她孙子在玩魔术时.\N跟我讲过这句话.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her grandson does the magic tricks.\NHe told me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:36.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但这是史密斯先生说的.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was Mr. Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Harold?\N- He left a suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:42.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哈罗德?\N- 是他的遗言.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:48.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道, 它意思是,\N"我是一个寂寞的灵魂."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it means,\N''l am a lonely soul.''
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have to find Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我得去找库珀探员.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 到底怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Tremond's the one\Nwho told me about Harold Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:09.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是屈梦太太\N告诉我关于哈罗德·史密斯的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a grandson\Nand he said this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:12.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她有个孙子\N就是他告诉我那法文的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same words that are in\NHarold Smith's suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和哈罗德·史密斯的遗言\N一模一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:17.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,大概那个男孩\N跟哈罗德说过同样的话.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the boy\Nsaid the same thing to Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Harold's world was in his words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 他说的就是哈罗德的世界.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:22.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个遗言在透露\N一个信息.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suicide note has to be\Na message.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:24.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把我们带回到这里来.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt all leads back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty old. lt might take a second\Nif her grandson isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:31.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她年级很大了. 如果她孙子不在\N那就得等很久门才会开.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- May l help you?\N- ls Mrs. Tremond home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:37.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有什么事吗?\N- 屈梦太太在吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:40.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm Mrs. Tremond.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:42.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说\N你妈妈.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt must have been your mother\Nl spoke to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother?\NShe passed away three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:45.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈?\N她3年前就死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l live here alone, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:46.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在这里一个人住, 宝贝儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she was here. l spoke to her.\NAnd her grandson, he was here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:51.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 她在这儿住过. 我和她说过话.\N还有她孙子, 他当时也在的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我没有小孩啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l have no children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:54.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但他当时真的在啊.\N他们2个都在的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was here.\NThey both were.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:56.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 我们还是走吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, we'd better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna?\NAre you Donna Hayward?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:58.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜?\N你是唐娜·海沃德?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah.\N- Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的.\N- 请稍等.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've never seen her before in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:05.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前从来没见过她.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought you delivered meals here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:07.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你是送餐来这儿的.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:10.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗德死的第二天早上,\N我在信箱里发现了这个.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The morning after poor Harold died,\Nl found this in my mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我把它拿出来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l meant to turn it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:14.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是给你的.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- lt's Harold's handwriting.\N- Open it, Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:25.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是哈罗德的笔迹.\N- 打开它, 唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's Laura's diary,\Na page from her diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:38.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是劳拉的日记,\N其中的一页.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,读来听听.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:44.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"2月22日.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''February 22nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:47.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚做了个\N极奇怪的梦.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night l had\Nthe strangest dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was in a red room\Nwith a small man dressed in red
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:51.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我和一个穿红衣的小人\N在一个红色的房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:53.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个老男人坐在椅子上.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and an old man sitting in a chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我试图和他说话.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l tried to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanted to tell him who Bob is\Nbecause l thought he could help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:59.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想告诉他谁是鲍勃\N因为我觉得他能救我.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My words came out slow and odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:02.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我说话的语调变得又慢又古怪.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was frustrating trying to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,越使劲去说就越令人感到沮丧.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got up and walked to the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:08.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我站起来走向那个老男人.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:12.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我弯腰在他耳边\N悄悄把秘密告诉了他.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then l leaned over and whispered\Nthe secret in his ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,必须有人去制止鲍勃.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody has to stop Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bob's only afraid of one man,\Nhe told me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:22.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,鲍勃只害怕一个人,\N他和我说过一次.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:24.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人叫迈克.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man named Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wonder if this was Mike\Nin my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:28.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想我梦中的这人\N是不是迈克.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was only a dream,\Nl hope he heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:32.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就算这只是一个梦,\N我也希望他能听见我.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one in the real world\Nwould believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:35.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在现实世界\N没有一个人相信我.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,February 23rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:38.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,2月23日.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight is the night that l die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就是我的死期了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know l have to\Nbecause it's the only way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:45.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我必死无疑\N因为这是我唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to keep Bob away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:47.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,远离鲍勃的方式.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to tear him out\Nfrom inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:50.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也是唯一从内心将他\N撕毁的方法.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:54.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他要的是我,\N我能感觉到他的欲火.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know he wants me,\Nl can feel his fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if l die,\Nhe can't hurt me anymore.''
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:57.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但只有我死了,\N他就再也不能伤害我了."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:06.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉和我都做个相同的梦.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura and l had the same dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's impossible.\N- Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:09.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那不可能.\N- 是的, 真的.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy, take Donna home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,副警官, 送唐娜回家吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got to see Gerard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:17.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去看看杰勒德了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:34.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他已经完全脱水了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely dehydrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:37.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他的呼吸越来越困难\N他需要药.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His breathing is becoming\Nmore difficult. He needs that drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:39.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克.\N迈克, 和我说话.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mike.\NMike, l need you to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Any longer could kill him.\N- Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:43.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 再拖下去会要了他的命.\N- 迈克.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bob has killed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:51.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,鲍勃又杀人了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need to know something.\Nl need you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:55.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有些事我必须知道.\N我需要你的帮助.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:11:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bob was in my dream, Laura Palmer\Nwas in my dream, so were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:11:00.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我梦见过鲍勃,\N劳拉·帕尔默，还有你.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Laura dreamt about me\Nthe night before she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:03.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而劳拉死的前一晚\N也梦见了我.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same dream that l had.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:05.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和我一样的梦.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need to unlock that.\Nl need-- The answer is inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:08.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要解开它.\N我必须-- 答案就在我的内心深处.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bob and l,\Nwhen we were killing together,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:13.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,鲍勃和我,\N我们以前一起杀人的时候,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was this perfect relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:17.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是最佳伙伴,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,appetite,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:19.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欲望,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:21.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,满足,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,satisfaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:23.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个金色的圆圈.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a golden circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:25.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个金色的圆圈.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A golden circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:30.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是戒指.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的戒指.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l gave my ring to the Giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我把我的戒指给了那个巨人.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is known to us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:37.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道他在这儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he's real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:38.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么他是真实的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As real as l.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:42.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就我和一样真实.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can help you find Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:46.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他能帮你找到鲍勃.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How?\N- You must ask him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:50.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么找?\N- 你必须要先问他.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do l do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我要怎么做呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you have all the clues you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:59.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,你需要的所有线索都已经有了 .
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is not here my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:05.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友，答案并不在这里.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:09.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而是在这里.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:11.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:16.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太多太多责任了.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:46.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That milk will cool down on you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:51.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你让牛奶凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's getting warmer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:55.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是它现在又渐渐回温了.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Getting warmer now.''
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:01.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"现在又渐渐回温了."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Box and tag everything\Nin these drawers. Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:14.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你把这抽屉里的所有东西\N都贴上标签. 所有东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coop, we found his telephone records.\NLook at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:18.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库, 我们找到了这个通话记录.\N看看这个.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The night Laura died.\NTelephone call Leland told us about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉死的那晚.\N这就是利兰跟我们提起的那个电话.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben called her number\Nfrom this office.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:25.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本在办公室这儿\N打电话给她.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,白狐貍.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, white, dead and stuffed.\NMaddy was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:30.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊, 白色, 标本和填塞物.\N马蒂来过这儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:34.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为本是在办公室这里杀了她\N然后再运到瀑布那里的.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think Ben killed her in this office,\Nthen took her to the waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed Laura\Nand he killed Maddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:38.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了劳拉\N和马蒂.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madeleine Ferguson died\Nthe night before last
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,马德琳·弗格逊是\N前晚遇害的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between 1 0 p.m. and midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在10点和子夜之间.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fits. We didn't take Ben in\Nuntil after midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,完全吻合. 我们是在子夜之后\N才把本抓进去的.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's as close as l can cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那已经足够我把它打断了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben Horne's blood test.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本·荷恩的血液检验报告.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A couple of minutes,\Nl'll have this up to code.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,2分钟就好了,\N我很快会把它们编好码.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tweaking the sensors, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:03.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把传感器拼好, 差不多了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want your sprinklers\Nto be overly jumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:05.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别指望你这个灭火洒水头\N会自己灵敏的反应.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta set it just so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,必须进行设置才行的.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanna talk about my child,\Nour baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:11.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想谈谈关于我孩子的事,\N我们的宝宝.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Maybe.\N- Maybe what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 也许吧.\N- 也许什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it is our baby\Nand maybe it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:18.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是我们的孩子\N也许不是.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dick?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,基巴吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my Lord, is he the father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:22.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 我的主啊, 他是爸爸吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first l thought\Nyou were the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:25.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始我以为\N你是爸爸.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then you said\Nyou didn't have any sperms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:28.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但然后你说\N你都没有任何精子.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then l thought it was Dick\Nbut now you say your sperms are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:34.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,之后我就想是基巴的\N但现在你说你的精子又回来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So as far as l can tell,\Nit's a 50-50 proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:38.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我最多只能说,\N你们各占50%的机会.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:43.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪, 你去哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:45.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:49.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你在给谁打电话?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to speak to Richard Tremayne,\NMen's Fashions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:53.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我找理查·屈梅恩,\N男装部的.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的, I我等着.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l'll hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:58.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会伤害他吧, 你会吗, 安迪?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't hurt him, will you, Andy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tremayne, Brennan.\NAndy Brennan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:03.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,屈梅恩, 布伦南.\N安迪·布伦南.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:05.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须谈谈.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, if you're not too busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:08.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是, 如果你不太忙的话.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tojamura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:24.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,托吉麻辣先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴你来电问候.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice of you to come calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:29.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你坐牢了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊, 嗯,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a momentary inconvenience,\Nl assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:36.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只是个暂时的困境,\N我向你保证.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have papers to sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:39.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有文件要签署.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ghostwood contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:43.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,格斯伍的合约.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tojamura-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:47.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,托吉麻辣先生,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm afraid there has been a snag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:51.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我恐怕现在有了点小小的障碍.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A snag?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:52.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,障碍?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforeseen difficulties.\NSome legal in nature, others...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:56.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,意料之外的问题.\N一些相关法律, 还有其他什么的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm unable to sign\Nthe Ghostwood agreement at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:02.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能在这个时候\N签格斯伍协议书.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you will return\Nmy five million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:06.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你要退还我\N5百万美元.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:11.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊, 我也想把钱退还给你.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l want to return your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:13.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想签合约.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to sign the contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tojamura-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:16.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,托吉麻辣先生,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:19.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所见的,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am incarcerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在被囚禁了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Falsely accused,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,被人诬告了,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but my brother, the boy genius,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:29.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我弟弟, 绝顶聪明的家伙,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is out looking for a better lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:33.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正在为我找更好的律师.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And until justice is done,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:36.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后只要审判一结束,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until l am able to breathe the air\Nthat free men breathe,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.31,0:16:42.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我就能够从新呼吸\N自由人的空气了,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l plead with you for understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:47.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我恳求你能理解.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the long, dark night\Nof my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:55.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我灵魂中\N黑暗而漫长的一夜.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to seek that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:58.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是时候在黑夜里...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...tiny flickering flame within.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:03.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...去寻找那点点忽闪而微弱的火焰了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me,\Nl've been very emotional lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:07.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我吧,\N我最近非常情绪化.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:23.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Benjamin Horne.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:26.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本杰明·荷恩.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a slimy rat bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:31.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是个油嘴滑舌的卑鄙小人，混帐家伙.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l intend to make whatever\Nremains of your pathetic existence
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:35.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但无论如何，我还是打算\N保住你这条贱命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好让你继续存在于这个人间地狱.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:40.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊, 凯萨琳.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:44.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 我的神啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:46.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你终于来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 凯萨琳.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine, Catherine,\Ntell Sheriff Truman
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:54.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳, 凯萨琳,\N快去告诉杜鲁门警长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about the night\Nthat we spent together
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:57.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那晚\N我们是一起过的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the night that Laura was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:18:00.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉被杀的那晚.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to beg?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:04.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要我乞求吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to beg?\NBecause l'll beg.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:06.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要我乞求吗?\N因为我会的.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you sign Ghostwood\Nand the mill over to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:10.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你会把格斯伍和锯木厂\N签回给我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻签.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clever disguise, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:19.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的易容术很聪明, 凯萨琳.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:21.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太有才华了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signed, sealed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:25.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,签字, 盖印
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:28.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,送达.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you'll tell the sheriff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:31.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 你会去告诉杜鲁门警长了吗, 嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll tell the sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你会告诉警长的.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会考虑的.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine. Catherine, wait a minute.\NWait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:39.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳. 凯萨琳, 等会儿.\N等等.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's the truth, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:43.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟, 那是事实啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Ben, we've spent our entire\Nadult lives lying to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:47.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呀, 本, 我们都已经花了\N一生去彼此欺骗.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why spoil it with the truth now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,犯得着在这会儿以真相来破坏气氛吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:54.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:01.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so happy you stopped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:06.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你来拜访我真高兴.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't had the time\Nto just sit down and talk for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:11.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们好久都没\N坐下来仔细聊过了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May l get you a glass of lemonade?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你倒杯柠檬水怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:17.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不了, 谢了, 帕尔默先生.\N我马上要走了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks, Mr. Palmer.\Nl only have a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for Maddy. lt's a tape\Nof a song we did with James.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:21.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是给马蒂的. 是一盘我们\N和詹姆斯一起录的歌.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want her to have a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:23.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我复制了一份给她.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very sweet of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:25.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你太贴心了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me all about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:27.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她和我讲过这事儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it was\Na very enjoyable experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:30.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她说那是个\N非常好玩的体验.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if you could mail it to her,\Nl'd really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:34.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,总之, 如果你能寄给她的话,\N我就真的很感激了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it won't be any problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:37.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没事, 一点问题也没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:43.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不妥吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那副太阳镜.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were Laura's.\NMaddy gave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:52.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是劳拉的.\N马蒂把它给了我.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought they looked familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得看起来眼熟.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Palmer,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:12.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,帕尔默先生,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did you know\Nthat they found Laura's secret diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:17.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他们\N找到了劳拉的秘密日记吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diary? Yes,\Nthey took it from her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:22.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,日记? 知道,\N他们是从她房间拿走的.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not the one the police found.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:25.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 不是警察拿走的那本.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:27.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她还有另外一本.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't even know about it,\Ndid you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:30.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,连我都不知道,\N你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She gave it to a man\Nnamed Harold Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:35.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她给了一个叫\N哈罗德·史密斯的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harold killed himself a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:40.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗德几天前自杀死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police found it in his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:42.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,警察在他的公寓里找到了它.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:44.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 我的天啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:47.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我一点儿也不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wish l knew what was in it,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:51.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真想知道里面写了什么,\N你说呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think about Laura all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:54.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我整天想起劳拉.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:01.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 失陪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:06.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,喂?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Beth, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:10.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是你, 贝丝, 怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:13.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有, 从昨天起.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Beth. l took Maddy\Nto the bus station myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:16.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定, 贝丝. 是我亲自\N送马蒂去车站的.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:19.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 我--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sure there must be some\Nperfectly reasonable explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:23.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想她肯定\N有什么别的事要去办吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.\Nl'll call you immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:25.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 好的.\N我会及时给你打电话的,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:27.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一小时内.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:28.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再见, 贝丝.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:39.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,马蒂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's the strangest thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪事了.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never made it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她一直没有回家.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:46.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 天啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, don't you worry\Nabout a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:56.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 你不是\N很焦虑吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll get us some lemonade
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.59,0:21:59.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我去倒点柠檬水来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll sit down\Nand give it a think
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.98,0:22:03.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后坐下来\N好好思量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll work the problem out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:06.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再一起把问题给解决掉.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:08.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一起解决掉.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l knew she was expecting us,\Nl mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:50.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白她是希望我们,\N我意思是--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess l was selfish.\Nl thought l could see her anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:52.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我很自私.\N我以为我能随时见到她.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missoula's not that far away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:54.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,密苏拉离这儿不远吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, you're taking this much\Ntoo much to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:22:58.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 你想这个想太多了\N别胡思乱想了.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sure she's just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.93,0:23:01.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定她平安无事的.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know the cure for what ails you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.93,0:23:05.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道怎样去安抚你内心的苦闷.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's simple, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.63,0:23:06.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很简单, 真的.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt always makes me feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:09.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它总是能让我心情好起来.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.60,0:23:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May we have this dance...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.88,0:23:55.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们来跳这个舞吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...please?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.57,0:23:57.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...请?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.40,0:24:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.60,0:24:38.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你留在那儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.00,0:24:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.21,0:24:48.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.50,0:24:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland, we need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.82,0:24:50.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰, 我们需要你的协助.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.70,0:24:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.90,0:24:52.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.20,0:24:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- There's been another murder.\N- Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.47,0:24:54.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 又发生了一起凶杀案.\N- 噢, 我的天啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.90,0:24:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't tell you why or how but we need\Nyour help and we need it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.16,0:24:59.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道该怎样说才好\N反正我们需要你的协助，马上.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.10,0:25:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, anything, certainly.\NLet me get my coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.42,0:25:02.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的, 这个当然, 没问题的.\N我去拿大衣.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.90,0:25:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.25,0:25:12.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,马蒂.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.20,0:25:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.20,0:25:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.50,0:25:36.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?\N发生什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.00,0:25:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- lt's Maddy.\N- What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.28,0:25:40.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是马蒂.\N- 她怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.30,0:25:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.54,0:25:41.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.30,0:25:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was the same killer.\NThe same one who killed Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.58,0:25:46.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是同一个凶手.\N杀害劳拉的同一个凶手.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.00,0:25:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard Mr. Palmer get a phone call\Nfrom her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.32,0:25:53.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我听见帕尔默先生\N和她妈妈在讲电话.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.10,0:25:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said\Nshe hadn't gotten home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.32,0:25:55.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她说\N她还没回到家.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.10,0:25:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they came over to talk to him,\NSheriff Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.28,0:25:57.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后他们就来找他了,\N杜鲁门警长.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.70,0:25:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- We could've helped her.\N- How?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.97,0:25:59.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们本来可以救她的.\N- 怎么救?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.80,0:26:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- We could've helped her.\N- How?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.06,0:26:01.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们本来可以救她的.\N- 怎么救?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.50,0:26:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.80,0:26:03.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.40,0:26:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- This is no good.\N- What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.71,0:26:08.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这样不好.\N- 你是指什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.20,0:26:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean us?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.27,0:26:11.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们么?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.80,0:26:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l gotta go.\N- James, it's not our fault, don't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.01,0:26:17.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我得走了.\N- 詹姆斯, 那不是我们的错, 别走.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.70,0:26:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt doesn't matter, don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.01,0:26:19.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不重要了, 难道你还不懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.70,0:26:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing we do matters.\NNothing's ever gonna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.01,0:26:23.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们做什么.\N都不会改变命运.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.00,0:26:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt doesn't matter if we're happy\Nand the rest of the world goes to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.31,0:26:27.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们快乐与否，或世界末日\N都无关紧要了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.70,0:26:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,James, don't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.06,0:26:32.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯, 别走.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.00,0:26:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,James, don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.27,0:26:35.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯, 不要离开我!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.10,0:27:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.36,0:27:21.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.30,0:27:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.58,0:27:24.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.80,0:27:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we here, Agent Cooper?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.06,0:27:28.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们为什么在这儿, 库珀探员?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.60,0:27:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls someone meeting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.70,0:27:31.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要见什么人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.90,0:27:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.96,0:27:33.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.40,0:27:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls it the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.61,0:27:35.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,见凶手?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.30,0:27:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know. Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.57,0:27:38.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道. 也许吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.10,0:27:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ed, glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.39,0:27:43.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德, 很高兴你来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.80,0:27:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need everyone's help\Nto clear the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.08,0:27:46.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要大家帮忙\N整理一下这个空间.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.60,0:27:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need a large space in the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.82,0:27:49.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在房的中间留出一块大空地.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.80,0:27:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.12,0:27:52.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.90,0:28:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hail, hail. The gang's all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.24,0:28:06.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎, 欢迎. 大伙儿都到齐了.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.00,0:28:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby, why don't you wheel Leo\Nback over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.24,0:28:11.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比, 你干嘛不把里欧\N推到那边去呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.50,0:28:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay very, very quiet, you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.76,0:28:13.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,非常非常安静的, 在那边呆着, 听懂了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.40,0:28:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give yourself a raise, Hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.71,0:28:15.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以一边玩去了, 豪克.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.00,0:28:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, two days ago\Na young woman was found murdered
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.36,0:28:26.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们, 2天前\N一位年轻的女士被人谋杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.30,0:28:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the same individual,\Nl believe, responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.57,0:28:28.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信,\N是杀害劳拉·帕尔默的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.60,0:28:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the death of Laura Palmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.83,0:28:31.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,同一个人干的.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.70,0:28:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have reason to believe\Nthat the killer is in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.04,0:28:36.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有理由相信这个凶手\N就在这间房子里.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.70,0:28:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a member of the Bureau,\Nl spend most of my time
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.00,0:28:39.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,作为警方的一份子,\N我花了大量时间
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.40,0:28:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,seeking simple answers\Nto difficult questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.73,0:28:42.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在错综复杂的问题中\N寻找答案.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.80,0:28:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln the pursuit of Laura's killer,\Nl have employed Bureau guidelines,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.04,0:28:46.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在追查杀劳拉的凶手时,\N我除了按规章办事,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.60,0:28:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,deductive technique,\NTibetan method, instinct and luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.77,0:28:52.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,使用推理技术,\N还有藏民的方法, 也依靠直觉和运气.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.70,0:28:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now l find myself\Nin need of something new,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.90,0:28:55.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在我发现自己\N的确需要求助于新事物了,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.50,0:29:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which for lack of a better word\Nwe shall call ''magic.''
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.72,0:29:00.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么比我们用『魔术』\N这个词更贴切了."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.90,0:29:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like us to hum?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.15,0:29:07.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要我们唸唸有词吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.90,0:29:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Tibetan chant, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.15,0:29:10.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是首藏族圣诗呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.90,0:29:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think it's going terrifically well,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.27,0:29:15.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得形势大好啊,\N你觉得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.10,0:29:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.40,0:29:18.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那现在干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.70,0:29:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, l'm not completely sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.05,0:29:21.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 我不完全肯定.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.40,0:29:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.53,0:29:25.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个人没到.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.20,0:29:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.61,0:29:34.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我们来晚了.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.10,0:29:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Briggs, right on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.39,0:29:38.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,布里格斯少校, 来的正好.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.10,0:29:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.25,0:29:40.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我正开车回家.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.10,0:29:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This kind gentleman\Nflagged me down,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.34,0:29:43.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这位好好先生\N把我截停了,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.00,0:29:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,asked if l could drive him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.25,0:29:46.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请我送他到这来.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.10,0:30:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know that gum.\Nl used to chew it when l was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.43,0:30:04.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这口香糖.\N我小的时候吃过.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.30,0:30:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my most favorite gum\Nin the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.47,0:30:06.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是这个世界上我最喜欢\N的口香糖.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.00,0:30:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That gum you like\Nis going to come back in style.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.21,0:30:12.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它的口味\N始终如一.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.40,0:30:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.67,0:30:31.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是我父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.10,0:30:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.28,0:30:33.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.00,0:31:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben Horne,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.28,0:31:20.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本·荷恩,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.00,0:31:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l would like you to accompany me\Nto the sheriff's station.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.41,0:31:22.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你陪我\N一同会警局.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.10,0:31:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might like to bring along\NLeland Palmer as your attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.36,0:31:27.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以带上利兰·帕尔默一同\N作为你的律师.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.80,0:32:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take him down to interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.97,0:32:18.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把他带到审讯室.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.00,0:32:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper,\Nis he going to be charged?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.27,0:32:24.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀探员,\N他会被起诉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.10,0:32:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.40,0:32:25.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.60,0:32:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then l think l'd like to begin bail\Nproceedings as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.05,0:32:29.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我想我还是尽快\N开始准备保释程序.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.00,0:32:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll have his day in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.27,0:32:31.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他很快就要上法庭了.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.00,0:32:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.26,0:32:35.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.80,0:32:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be all right, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.12,0:32:58.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,会没事的, 本.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.00,0:33:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk, take Ben upstairs\Nand release him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.23,0:33:18.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,豪克, 带本上楼\N释放他吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.30,0:33:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Leland?\N- That's not Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.58,0:33:20.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 利兰?\N- 那个已经不是利兰了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.20,0:33:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.53,0:33:25.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么知道的?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.00,0:33:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura told me in her dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.31,0:33:27.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉在梦中告诉我的.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.60,0:33:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna need\Na lot stronger evidence than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.96,0:33:30.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须\N要找到更多有力的证据.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.90,0:33:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a confession, Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.44,0:33:32.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让他自招怎样, 哈里?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.40,0:33:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the right to an attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.69,0:33:36.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你有权请律师.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.50,0:33:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you cannot afford an attorney,\None will be appointed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.78,0:33:40.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你支付不起律师,\N我们将会为你指定一名.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.30,0:33:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. l suppose you wanna\Nask him some questions, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.68,0:33:59.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 对了. 我猜你肯定\N有问题问他, 哼?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.60,0:34:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you kill Laura Palmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.98,0:34:02.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是你杀了劳拉·帕尔默?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.00,0:34:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.41,0:34:09.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是『是』的意思.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.10,0:34:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about Madeleine Ferguson?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.45,0:34:12.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那马德琳·弗格逊呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.10,0:34:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What do you think?\N- l'm asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.49,0:34:14.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你觉得呢?\N- 我在问你呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.20,0:34:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What do you think?\N- Answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.44,0:34:16.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你觉得呢?\N- 回答问题.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.20,0:34:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gosh, gee, gee whiz.\Nl guess l kind of sort of did.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.31,0:34:19.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 糟了, 哇, 妈妈呀.\N我想或许大概是我干的吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.50,0:34:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have this thing for knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.87,0:34:21.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你可是有把柄在我手上啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.60,0:34:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like what happened to you\Nin Pittsburgh that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.92,0:34:24.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就像你上次\N在匹兹堡发生的那样.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.50,0:34:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Cooper?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.91,0:34:26.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哼, 库珀?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.40,0:34:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.69,0:34:30.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.30,0:34:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland, Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.52,0:34:32.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰, 利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.70,0:34:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been a good vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.95,0:34:34.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都是辆好车
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.80,0:34:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l've enjoyed the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.17,0:34:37.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可享受开着你到处跑了.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.20,0:34:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now he's weak and full of holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.56,0:34:39.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但他现在已经满目疮痍，也废了.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.60,0:34:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's almost nearly time\Nto shuffle off to Buffalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.99,0:34:43.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也差不多是时候\N把他扔到水牛城了.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.90,0:34:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Leland know\Nwhat you've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.25,0:34:45.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰知道\N你所做的一切吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.00,0:34:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland's a babe in the woods
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.38,0:34:48.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰不过是个幼稚无知的人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.40,0:34:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a large hole\Nwhere his conscience used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.76,0:34:52.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他身上有个大洞\N曾经装着他的良心.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.70,0:34:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when l go, children,\Nl will pull that ripcord
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.07,0:34:56.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当我进去后, 我的儿啊,\N我就把它封锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.80,0:35:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you watch Leland, remember.\NWatch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.06,0:35:00.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我走着瞧，利兰, 记住.\N小心点.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.60,0:35:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.77,0:35:02.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不用太久.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.00,0:35:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.41,0:35:13.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,足够证据了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.40,0:35:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dick,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.65,0:35:38.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,基巴,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.10,0:35:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,could you come with me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.44,0:35:40.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,能跟我来一下吗, 这边请?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.40,0:35:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here's how\Nthis is going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.73,0:35:49.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 现在\N给我听着.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.80,0:35:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm going to keep my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.12,0:35:52.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算要这个孩子.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.50,0:35:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not open for discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.77,0:35:55.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何商量的余地.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.90,0:35:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l see.\N- Be quiet, let her talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.29,0:35:59.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我知道.\N- 安静点, 让他说完.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.10,0:36:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a light?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.46,0:36:01.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,诱火吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.20,0:36:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.55,0:36:08.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.80,0:36:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.19,0:36:11.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.20,0:36:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.58,0:36:15.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个办法去处理这件事.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.50,0:36:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a test to determine\Nthe blood type of the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.89,0:36:19.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会通过血型测试\N来最后决定谁是爸爸.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.50,0:36:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt could be you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.75,0:36:21.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那可能是你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.50,0:36:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or it could be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.80,0:36:23.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也有可你能是你.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.90,0:36:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't be doing this test\Nuntil after the baby is born,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.14,0:36:27.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是必须等宝宝出生后\N他们才会进行测试,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.80,0:36:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during which time\Nl expect complete cooperation
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.14,0:36:31.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在宝宝出生之前的这段时间\N我希望你们2位先生
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.00,0:36:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from each of you two gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.31,0:36:33.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,能充分配合.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.60,0:36:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you say, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.96,0:36:36.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说, 露西.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.20,0:36:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, it is your baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.66,0:36:38.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说, 反正是你的孩子.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.30,0:36:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.57,0:36:40.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.90,0:36:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben Horne's blood test,\Nhe's the wrong type.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.30,0:36:53.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本·荷恩的血液测试说明,\N他的血型不吻合.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.20,0:36:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, the answer was right in front\Nof me from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.64,0:36:56.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 答案其实一开始\N就已经在我眼前了.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.70,0:36:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did the little man do\Nin my dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.12,0:36:59.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还记得那个小侏儒在我梦里\N干什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.90,0:37:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He danced.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.25,0:37:03.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他在跳舞.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.40,0:37:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Laura's death,\NLeland danced compulsively.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.68,0:37:07.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉死后,\N利兰就开始强迫性的跳舞.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.90,0:37:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were told that Bob the killer\Nwas a gray-haired man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.20,0:37:10.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它还预示我们\N那个叫鲍勃的凶手有一头灰发.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.20,0:37:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Leland killed Jacques,\Nhis hair turned gray overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.50,0:37:13.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当利兰杀了雅克后,\N他就一夜灰头了.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.40,0:37:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland said when he was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.72,0:37:15.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰说他小时候
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.00,0:37:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the gray-haired man next door\Nwas named Robertson.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.41,0:37:17.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个住他隔壁的灰发人\N叫罗伯逊.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.70,0:37:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mike said the people Bob inhabited\Nwere his children.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.15,0:37:20.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克则说鲍勃所寄生的那个肉身\N就是他的孩子.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.70,0:37:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robertson, son of Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.06,0:37:23.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,罗伯的儿子，罗伯逊.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.50,0:37:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The letters under the finger nails:\NR, O, B, T.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.88,0:37:26.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那些在指甲下的字母:\NR, O, B, T.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.10,0:37:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bob was spelling his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.49,0:37:27.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,鲍勃在拼自己的名字.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.60,0:37:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A signature on a demon self-portrait.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.10,0:37:30.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,签名是魔鬼的自述.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.50,0:37:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.83,0:37:32.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那他为什么要杀她?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.90,0:37:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura was writing about Bob\Nin her diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.40,0:37:34.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉在她的日记里\N写下了关于鲍勃的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.00,0:37:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland found it, ripped out the pages.\NShe knew he was on to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.48,0:37:37.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰发现了, 并把那几页撕了下来.\N她就知道被盯上了.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.40,0:37:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was Leland who placed that call\Nfrom Ben Horne's office
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.83,0:37:40.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉死那晚接到的电话\N就是利兰在
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.10,0:37:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to Laura the night she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.48,0:37:41.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本·荷恩办公室打出去的.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.80,0:37:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the third man\Noutside Jacques' cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.13,0:37:44.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那晚，站在雅克小木屋窗外\N的神秘人，就是他.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.20,0:37:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took the girls to the train car. lt was\Nhis blood we found not Ben Horne's.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.48,0:37:48.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是他把女孩们绑架到火车厢那里.\N案发现场的血迹是他的，而不是本·荷恩的.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.60,0:37:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Then why kill Maddy?\N- Maybe she reminded him of Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.99,0:37:52.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那为什么还要杀马蒂?\N- 或许她令他想起了劳拉.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.10,0:37:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maddy was going home.\NHe couldn't bear to part with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.60,0:37:55.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,马蒂要回家了.\N他不能承受和她分开的事实.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.10,0:37:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to relive the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.51,0:37:57.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他想在次重温杀戮的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.90,0:37:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or maybe she realized\NBob was the killer and he found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.21,0:38:00.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,又或许是她意识到鲍勃\N就是凶手，然后被他发现了.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.60,0:38:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.90,0:38:03.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在, 这个鲍勃.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.30,0:38:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't really exist.\Nl mean, Leland is just crazy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.85,0:38:07.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他不能真的存在.\N我是说, 只能说利兰疯了, 不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.80,0:38:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through the dark of futures past,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.24,0:38:11.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}穿越未来过去的黑暗,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.10,0:38:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the magician longs to see
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.41,0:38:14.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}魔术师渴望见到{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.30,0:38:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One chants out between two worlds
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.80,0:38:18.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}在2个世界之间传出的1首圣歌{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.10,0:38:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire walk with me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.50,0:38:21.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}与火同行{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.00,0:38:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll catch you with my death bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.45,0:38:26.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会把你抓进我的死亡之袋.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.20,0:38:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may think l've gone insane
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.53,0:38:29.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我发疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.90,0:38:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but l promise l will kill again!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.23,0:38:33.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我保证我会再开杀戒!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.70,0:39:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.07,0:39:07.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 快来.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.80,0:39:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.16,0:39:09.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.30,0:39:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.68,0:39:13.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.10,0:39:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.50,0:39:15.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.90,0:39:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry. Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.15,0:39:18.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里. 利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.90,0:39:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.27,0:39:28.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,快叫救护车.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.70,0:39:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God, Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.18,0:39:33.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 天啊, 劳拉.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.20,0:39:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.62,0:39:35.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是我杀了她.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.90,0:39:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God. l killed my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.40,0:39:39.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊, 我的天啊. 我杀了我的女儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.20,0:39:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.70,0:39:41.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还蒙在鼓里.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.90,0:39:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.39,0:39:43.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉, 宽恕我吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.10,0:39:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.57,0:39:45.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,宽恕我吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.40,0:39:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, God.\N- lt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.87,0:39:48.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 啊, 天啊.\N- 好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.10,0:39:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.43,0:39:50.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.80,0:39:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was just a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.12,0:39:54.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那时我还是个小孩.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.90,0:39:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l saw him in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.25,0:39:57.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在梦里见到了他.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.40,0:40:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wanted to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.73,0:40:00.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他说他想和我玩.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.10,0:40:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He opened me and l invited him\Nand he came inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.57,0:40:06.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他把我打开了，而我也邀请他了\N他就这样侵占了我的内心.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.80,0:40:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.04,0:40:08.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他进去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.10,0:40:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he was inside, l didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.47,0:40:12.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当他来的时候, 我察觉不到.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.70,0:40:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when he was gone,\Nl couldn't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.17,0:40:18.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当他走了,\N我也什么都不记得了.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.90,0:40:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made me do things...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.34,0:40:20.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他控制了我，去做那些...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.10,0:40:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.64,0:40:23.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...那些可怕的事情.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.20,0:40:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wanted lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.68,0:40:26.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他说他想要生命,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.00,0:40:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he wanted others.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.46,0:40:27.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别人的生命.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.70,0:40:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Others that they could use\Nlike they used me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.16,0:40:32.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,任意去使用别人的生命\N就像现在用我的一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.40,0:40:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Laura?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.67,0:40:35.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就像劳拉?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.10,0:40:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.41,0:40:36.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要她.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.60,0:40:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted Laura,\Nbut she was strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.02,0:40:40.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要劳拉,\N但她很坚强.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.10,0:40:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She fought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.36,0:40:42.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她反抗他们.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.00,0:40:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.28,0:40:44.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她不让他们侵占她的肉身.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.80,0:40:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.14,0:40:47.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊, 上帝啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.10,0:40:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They had me kill that girl, Theresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.49,0:40:50.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是他们让我杀了那个女孩的, 杜丽莎.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.50,0:40:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they-- They said...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.96,0:40:56.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们-- 他们还说...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.10,0:40:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if l didn't give them Laura,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.44,0:40:59.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...如果我不把劳拉给他们,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.10,0:41:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'd have me kill her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.44,0:41:02.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也会控制我杀了她.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.80,0:41:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she wouldn't let them in?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.17,0:41:05.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但她不会让他们侵占的?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.30,0:41:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'd die\Nbefore she let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.65,0:41:12.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她说她宁愿死\N也不愿意给他们侵占.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.30,0:41:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they made me kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.56,0:41:16.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后他们就要我杀了她.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.40,0:41:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God, have mercy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.86,0:41:21.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 上帝啊, 可怜可怜我吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.00,0:41:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have l done?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.46,0:41:24.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看我都做了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.30,0:41:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have l done?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.64,0:41:28.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看我都做了什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.40,0:41:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God, l love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.72,0:41:33.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊, 天啊, 我是爱她的.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.90,0:41:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l loved her with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.28,0:41:36.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我全心全意的爱着她.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.80,0:41:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My angel, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.19,0:41:41.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天使, 宽恕我吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.40,0:41:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.88,0:41:48.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.20,0:41:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland, the time has come\Nfor you to seek the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.49,0:41:58.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰, 时间会为你\N寻求解脱之路.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.50,0:42:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your soul has set you\Nface to face with a clear light
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.79,0:42:02.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂以明灯\N引领你直面一切
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.90,0:42:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you are now about to experience it\Nin its reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.22,0:42:05.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在进入它的世界\N去好好体验吧,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.40,0:42:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wherein all things are like the void\Nand cloudless sky
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.91,0:42:09.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里面空无一人\N万里无云
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.50,0:42:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the naked, spotless intellect\Nis like a transparent vacuum
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.91,0:42:14.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,赤裸裸一望无际, 圣洁无暇的灵悟\N犹如真空般清澈透明
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.40,0:42:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without circumference or center.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.86,0:42:17.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,无始无终.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.10,0:42:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland, in this moment,\Nknow yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.42,0:42:21.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰, 这一刻,\N感悟你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.20,0:42:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and abide in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.55,0:42:23.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,并坚持着那种状态.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.60,0:42:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look to the light, Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.03,0:42:28.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,注视那盏明灯, 利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.50,0:42:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.98,0:42:30.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,找到它.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.40,0:42:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.81,0:42:33.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到它了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.40,0:42:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lnto the light, Leland.\Nlnto the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.80,0:42:38.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在BE436A06里面, 利兰.\N在BE436A06里.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.60,0:42:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.11,0:42:42.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到她了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.90,0:42:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.28,0:42:46.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她在那里.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.90,0:42:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lnto the light, Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.23,0:42:48.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在36F55044里, 利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.90,0:42:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.27,0:42:51.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她美丽极了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.80,0:42:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lnto the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.05,0:42:53.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在55F791D8里.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.00,0:42:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.35,0:42:58.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.60,0:43:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.05,0:43:01.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别害怕.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.60,0:44:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was completely insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.94,0:44:00.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他完全精神错乱了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.50,0:44:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.98,0:44:02.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真这么想吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.10,0:44:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But people saw Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.59,0:44:04.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但大家都看到鲍勃了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.10,0:44:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People saw him in visions:\NLaura, Maddy, Sarah Palmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.54,0:44:09.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她们都确实看见过他:\N劳拉, 马蒂, 莎拉·帕尔默.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.20,0:44:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen,\Nthere's more in heaven and earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.63,0:44:12.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们,\N其实这更像是我们以自己的哲学世界观...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.20,0:44:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...than is dreamt up in our philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.58,0:44:14.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...在天地间虚构出来的东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.90,0:44:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.37,0:44:16.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,阿门.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.00,0:44:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l've lived in these old woods\Nmost of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.50,0:44:21.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊, 我几乎在这老森林里\N渡过了大半生.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.60,0:44:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've seen some strange things\Nbut this is way off the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.10,0:44:26.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也见过一些奇怪的事\N但这次简直超乎想像.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.90,0:44:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm having a hard time believing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.36,0:44:29.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,实在无法理解.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.80,0:44:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, is it easier to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.23,0:44:31.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 如果只是解释为一个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.50,0:44:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a man would rape and murder\Nhis own daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.93,0:44:34.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,强奸和谋杀了自己的亲生女儿\N是不是更容易理解呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.70,0:44:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any more comforting?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.19,0:44:37.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,使人更易接受呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.30,0:44:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.84,0:44:39.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.10,0:44:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An evil that great\Nin this beautiful world...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.45,0:44:45.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个美丽的世界\N充满了邪恶...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.50,0:44:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...finally,\Ndoes it matter what the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.92,0:44:49.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...以致最后,\N原因是什么已经不重要了?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.90,0:44:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because it's our job to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.44,0:44:54.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 因为我们的工作就是警恶除奸.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.20,0:44:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.62,0:44:56.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.20,0:45:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's all Bob is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.66,0:45:04.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也许那就是鲍勃吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.20,0:45:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The evil that men do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.70,0:45:06.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一种引诱人犯罪的邪恶力量.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.30,0:45:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it doesn't matter\Nwhat we call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.83,0:45:09.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们称它做什么\N也不重要了.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.50,0:45:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.05,0:45:11.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也不一定.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.10,0:45:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he was real, if he was here,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.65,0:45:16.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果他是真实的呢, 如果他真的存在过呢,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.60,0:45:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we had him trapped
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.18,0:45:17.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们逮到过他
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.60,0:45:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he got away,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.13,0:45:20.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只是又让他给逃了,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.00,0:45:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where's Bob now?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.31,0:45:23.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,鲍勃现在在哪儿呢?
